Package net.proteusframework.core.locale.annotation Description

In order to use this in an IDE, you'll need to make sure you've configured the com.i2rd.locale.annotation.LocalizationAP AnnotationProcessor to run when you build your project.

In Eclipse you may need to enable ""Run this container's processors in batch mode" under "Advanced" for the Annotation Processor Factory Jar.
